source.name: U.S. Overseas Loans and Grants (Greenbook)
source.description: These data are U.S economic and military assistance by country from 1946 to 2011. This is the authoritative data set of U.S. foreign assistance. The data set is used to report U.S foreign assistance to Congress as required by the Foreign Assistance Act, Section 634.
